---
import ServiceLayout from '../../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Quantum Startup Mentoring"
  description="Expert guidance and support for quantum computing startups"
>
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Comprehensive Startup Support</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Strategic Planning</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Market analysis</li>
          <li>• Business model development</li>
          <li>• Growth strategy</li>
          <li>• Risk assessment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Investment Support</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Pitch deck preparation</li>
          <li>• Investor networking</li>
          <li>• Valuation guidance</li>
          <li>• Due diligence support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Technical Advisory</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Technology validation</li>
          <li>• Architecture review</li>
          <li>• Platform selection</li>
          <li>• Development guidance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-indigo-100 p-8 rounded-lg mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Mentorship Program</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Program Benefits</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Expert Guidance</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Access to industry veterans and technical experts</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Resource Access</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Cloud credits and development tools</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-2 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Network Growth</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Industry connections and partnership opportunities</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Program Structure</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <span class="font-semibold text-purple-600">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Initial Assessment</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Evaluate startup needs and potential</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <span class="font-semibold text-purple-600">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Strategy Development</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Create customized growth plan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <span class="font-semibold text-purple-600">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Ongoing Support</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Regular mentoring and guidance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <span class="font-semibold text-purple-600">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Growth Acceleration</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Scale and expand operations</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Success Stories</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">memQ</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Guided early-stage quantum memory startup memQ, during its participation as part of the first cohort at Compass Incubator. This has led to successful Series A funding round and strategic partnerships with major tech companies.</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-purple-600">Results: $3M funding secured • 3x team growth</div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Drip.co</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Supported development of innovative AI platform to support athlete hydration tracking and predictive dosing, leading to successful market entry and client acquisition.</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-purple-600">Results: 10+ enterprise clients • pitch-ready for future capital raising</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-purple-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Join Our Startup Program</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Ready to accelerate your quantum computing startup? Let's discuss how our mentoring program can help you achieve your goals.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors">
        Apply Now
      </a>
      <a href="/services/quantum/solutions" class="inline-block bg-white text-purple-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors">
        Explore Solutions
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
